A very "Winnie" Birthday 💛🤍💖

This nostalgic theme was so fun to put together! Our daughter asked for a "pink piglet party" with Winnie the Pooh and the rest of the friends. These sweet little details made her special day that much more memorable 💕

This theme would also be perfect for a gender neutral baby shower 🥰 Comment "Links" for items sent via DM!

12 days - that's how far apart these clips were taken. The purple shirt was 4 days pre-op and the pink shirt is 8 days post breast reduction. I'm still at the early stage of recovery and healing but I already believe this is the best thing I've ever done for myself 💕

If you can relate to this journey, please share your experiences below 🤍

#breastreduction #breastreductionsurgery #selflovejourney #bodyconfience #motherhoodjourney

Thank you for all the love and support since my last video 💕Prioritizing yourself is so important and rediscovering yourself during / after motherhood is incredibly empowering 🤍 

Confident mom era begins now 💫
